b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":1572,"category_name":"Important","pr_category_id":"5","title_name":"[Important] Regarding Goodwill Gesture Items for Purchasable Items Affected By System Changes","message":"<div>The weapon, crafting, and wyrmprint systems (and game elements related to these systems) will be changed in an update scheduled for late September. Along with these changes, players will be given various items as goodwill gestures, including for the materials used and eldwater spent in creating or obtaining the affected weapons and wyrmprints.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Further information on both the system changes and goodwill gesture details will be provided in an upcoming notification. Below, please find details regarding gestures that will be given to affected players for in-game Shop offerings that are or have been available in the past.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0For the purchase of the Storage Pack<\/div><div>\\u30fbChange:<\/div><div>Weapon and wyrmprint storage will be removed.<\/div><div>\\u30fbGoodwill Gesture:<\/div><div>300 wyrmite<\/div><div>Note: The Storage Pack will no longer be sold after <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1599804000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0For the purchase of Weapon Storage +5 or Wyrmprint Storage +5 storage expansions with diamantium or wyrmite<\/div><div>\\u30fbChange:<\/div><div>Weapon and wyrmprint storage will be removed.<\/div><div>\\u30fbGoodwill Gesture:<\/div><div>50 diamantium or wyrmite (whichever used) &times; times expanded<\/div><div>Note: Weapon Storage +5 and Wyrmprint Storage +5 will be removed from the Shop on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1599804000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0For the purchase of packs that include unbinding items like the Unbind Pack (Weapons) or Unbind Pack (Wyrmprints), including those currently available<\/div><div>\\u30fbChange:<\/div><div>Players will only be able to have one of each weapon and wyrmprint and can increase the number of each that can be equipped on team members by upgrading each weapon and wyrmprint.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>If a player has more than one of a particular weapon, the extras will be converted into materials or other items. In addition, certain weapons will be removed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>If a player has more than one of a particular wyrmprint, the extras will be used to unbind the wyrmprint or be converted into eldwater or other items.<\/div><div>\\u30fbGoodwill Gesture:<\/div><div>If players used any of the following unbinding items from purchased packs, they will receive the amount of these items used: Adamantite Ingot, Damascus Ingot, Steel Brick, Golden Key, and Silver Key.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0For players who have two Lucky Hanetsuki Paddle weapons from purchasing Lucky Hanetsuki Paddle Packs<\/div><div>\\u30fbChange:<\/div><div>Players will only be able to have one Lucky Hanetsuki Paddle weapon.<\/div><div>\\u30fbGoodwill Gesture:<\/div><div>The second Lucky Hanetsuki Paddle weapon will be exchanged for 120 wyrmite.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0For the purchase of Upgrade Pack (Weapons)<\/div><div>\\u30fbChange:<\/div><div>The relevant endeavors will be removed when the endeavor details are changed.<\/div><div>\\u30fbGoodwill Gesture:<\/div><div>Items rewarded for clearing an endeavor will be provided if:<\/div><div>1. you have not completed the endeavor, or<\/div><div>2. you have completed the endeavor but have not accepted the reward.<\/div><div>Please note that no additional rewards will be provided if you have already completed every endeavor and accepted every reward.<\/div><div>Note: The Upgrade Pack (Weapons) will no longer be sold after <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1599804000\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1599804000,"prev_article_id":"1344","next_article_id":"2585","image_path":"","update_time":1600224541}}}'